libxpudp - X-Plane UDP Library

libxpudp is not really a library but will be a set of stuff to help reading
and sending data From and To X-Plane using his UDP interface.

Supported versions of X-Plane:
  - 9.61RC2

Parsing a raw packet (directly from the buffer) is available.
It will return a struct with index and values[7] as a float.

Building a raw packet (directly from a struct with index and values[7] as float) is avaiable.
It will return a buffer to send directly.

Contact: rhaamo -at- gruik _dot_ at

